dfischer.utils

Class LogVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.LogVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LogVectorInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HttpLoadTest

    public class LogVector
extends java.lang.Object
implements LogVectorInterface
    Collect log output of a thread and dump it later in a safe way.
    Please note that each thread must use an own instance of this class.
    See Also:
    LogVectorInterface, ThreadSaveLogVector
